<description>Released as a TV special.
Based on http://anidb.net/cr10172 [Natsume Souseki]’s 1906 novel, which was one of Japan`s best-selling books. The novel included autobiographical elements: Natsume once taught in Matsuyama, where Uranari comes to teach.
Animator Akio Sugino "cleaned up" Monkey Punch`s designs.
Some sources credit Osamu Dezaki as the director`s "assistant".
A shorter version of "Botchan" was produced in 1986 as part of a series, "Animated Classics of Japanese Literature".
Alternate title: "The Young Master."</description>
